---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const skills = [
  { category: 'Infrastructure', items: ['Active Directory / Entra', 'Microsoft 365 / Azure', 'Networking'] },
  { category: 'Operations', items: ['User Lifecycle Management', 'IT Asset Management', 'Ticketing Systems (FreshService)', 'IT Compliance & Auditing'] },
  { category: 'Technical', items: ['PowerShell / Automation', 'Hardware Deployment & Imaging', 'Email Security & Compliance', 'Technical Documentation'] },
  { category: 'Other', items: ['Front-End Web Development', 'Applied AI for IT Ops', 'SOC 2 Audit Coordination', 'Cross-functional Communication'] },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Career"
  description="Ben Atkins â€” IT Support professional with 6+ years of enterprise experience."
>
  <header class="mb-12">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"
      style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--color-heading);"
    >
      Career
    </h1>
    <p style="color: var(--color-muted);">
      6+ years in enterprise IT across healthcare and financial sectors.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-10" style="color: var(--color-body);">

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        I've spent the last six years doing IT support and sysadmin work at places where
        things can't break â€” a medical center and a multi-site financial firm. The work
        ranges from hands-on troubleshooting to building out onboarding systems to keeping
        auditors happy.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
        What I care about most: making systems work well, cutting out inefficiency, and
        communicating clearly with people who aren't technical. I'm currently looking for my
        next role â€”
        <a href="/contact" class="text-[#a78bfa] underline hover:text-[#7c3aed] transition-colors duration-200">reach out</a>
        if you've got something.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Experience -->
    <section>
      <h2
        class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-6"
        style="color: var(--color-muted);"
      >
        Experience
      </h2>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">

        <!-- LBMC -->
        <div class="border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-lg font-semibold"
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--color-heading);"
              >
                Service Desk Specialist â†’ Senior Specialist
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-accent-light);">LBMC</p>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2a2a2a] whitespace-nowrap"
              style="color: var(--color-muted);"
            >
              2021 â€“ 2025
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm">
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Tier 1/2 support</strong> for a multi-site tax firm â€” 5 regional offices plus
              overseas contractors. Windows, O365, accounting software, access management, networking,
              hardware, AV systems. All routed through FreshService.
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Built end-to-end onboarding workflows</strong> across all LBMC companies â€” AD provisioning,
              security groups, hardware imaging, license procurement, badge integration. Coordinated
              with HR and department leads.
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">SOC 2 audit coordination</strong> â€” collected and organized audit evidence, documented
              offboarding procedures (AD revocation, license reclamation, badge deactivation).
              100% on-time delivery to external auditors.
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Monthly license audits</strong> that identified unused or redundant subscriptions across
              the org â€” drove real cost savings while maintaining compliance.
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Managed the service desk</strong> â€” distributed tickets, mentored team members on
              escalations, maintained &lt;1 hour response SLA across all queues.
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Built an IT onboarding program</strong> for international contractors â€” led orientation
              sessions on environment architecture, security protocols, auth procedures.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- VUMC -->
        <div class="border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-lg font-semibold"
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--color-heading);"
              >
                Field Project Technician
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-accent-light);">Vanderbilt University Medical Center</p>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2a2a2a] whitespace-nowrap"
              style="color: var(--color-muted);"
            >
              2018 â€“ 2020
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm">
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Field support across VUMC's main campus and clinics</strong> throughout Middle
              Tennessee â€” resolved end-user issues while keeping healthcare IT operations running.
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Led post-migration O365 support</strong> â€” troubleshooting, documentation, and
              escalation management for clinical and administrative staff.
            </li>
            <li class="leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#2a2a2a]">
              <strong style="color: var(--color-heading);">Deployed clinical workstations</strong> via PowerShell scripting for AD integration.
              Used Pegasus, Active Directory, and Tolero for asset tracking and KACE compliance.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <section>
      <h2
        class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-6"
        style="color: var(--color-muted);"
      >
        Skills
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {skills.map(group => (
          <div class="border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-lg p-5 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
            <h3
              class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-3"
              style="color: var(--color-accent-light); font-family: var(--font-display);"
            >
              {group.category}
            </h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {group.items.map(skill => (
                <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2a2a2a] text-[#d1d5db] font-medium">
                  {skill}
                </span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Education -->
    <section>
      <h2
        class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-6"
        style="color: var(--color-muted);"
      >
        Education
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">

        <div class="border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-lg p-5 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-base font-semibold"
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--color-heading);"
              >
                Nashville Software School
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-accent-light);">Front-End Web Development</p>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2a2a2a] whitespace-nowrap"
              style="color: var(--color-muted);"
            >
              2018
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm mt-2" style="color: var(--color-muted);">
            Intensive full-time program â€” HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, jQuery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-lg p-5 bg-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <h3
                class="text-base font-semibold"
                style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--color-heading);"
              >
                University of Tennessee
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-accent-light);">B.A. Psychology Â· Minor in Business Administration</p>
            </div>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2a2a2a] whitespace-nowrap"
              style="color: var(--color-muted);"
            >
              2013
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Resume download -->
    <section class="pt-2">
      <a
        href="/BJA-Resume.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-white transition-colors duration-200"
        style="background-color: var(--color-accent);"
        onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#6d28d9'"
        onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--color-accent)'"
      >
        <span>ðŸ“„</span> Download Resume (PDF)
      </a>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
